Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.87,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:52.86,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Space Academy\NMeeting Place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:18.13,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Exam\NNext Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.77,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa Asumi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:16.96,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa Asumi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.13,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Fuchuuya Shinnosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.84,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Astronaut Training Course\NExaminee Number\NKatou Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.86,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Female Changing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:32.35,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,One Step Toward the Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:36.30,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.30,0:25:00.14,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Memory of a Distant Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Year 1,Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:02.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:07.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very\Npretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:11.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:24.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That finishes off the examinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.75,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like all of you in the Astronaut Training Course...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...to please wait here in the classroom a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:10.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We will now be transferring you all to another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Take your belongings and proceed to the front of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.11,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Eh? We're going somewhere else now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:28.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the last exam earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Buses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:42.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now then, first find out and confirm\Nwhich bus you will be riding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What the heck is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I wonder where they're planning on taking us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Watch the chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your names are posted over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.79,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,, Bus 1, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,M-Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa, you're not on that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.19,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,She found me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:41.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the test too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:47.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?! You didn't say anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.96,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Boy, that really surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.79,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,For you to be taking the Space Academy test too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:01.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure that you would be\Ncontinuing your family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:03.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Like I could work in the fireworks business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why? I think it would suit you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:08.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:20.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like that's where we are headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This same rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well of course you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They've been on the news and in the papers a lot before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:57.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's a standard multi-stage rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.52,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...and you can find those in the books\Nyou're always carrying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:05.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Although it's not like I'm always watching you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Those of you in the back, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:22.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not telling you earlier, but I'm Tanaka,\Nan examiner for the Tokyo Space Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'll explain about the secondary examination\Nthat you are all about to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:32.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, wasn't the exam earlier the last of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:36.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Because there were so many successful applicants\Nfrom the primary examination...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...we quickly added a practical examination for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:43.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We have contacted your relatives for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so there is no need to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A practical exam now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:53.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Like this could be hurriedly prepared when there's so much detail put into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They're just trying to keep us all off-balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:03.79,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,All of you applicants will now enter\Nthe simulated residence module...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.71,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...and undergo a closed-environment adaptation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:11.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You will be allotted a gym suit in exchange for your examination application ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so change in your individual changing rooms and head for your assigned rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...not forgetting your room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:24.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The test will be explained to you in detail when you all arrive in your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:25.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any questions about anything so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:29.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,May I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:34.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:37.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Can that rocket fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.25,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Right now, this has become the Space Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:51.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...but this was originally the home of the Space Museum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:56.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so what you see there was made for all\Nof the children who visited to enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and it is nothing more than a full-scale model rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Model...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.35,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So there is no chance of it ever flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.44,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Are there any more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So this is where the next test will take place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Huh? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:23.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Does he think this is a sightseeing tour or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.84,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hmph, that guy will just fail straight out anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something stuck on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:44.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She's surprised because you don't have any eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:48.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Pretty unusual though, female applicants...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:53.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know. You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A walnut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:57.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can have one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to do any extravehicular activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you'd better strengthen your grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:06.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Since you're a girl, I won't say you have to use one hand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At least enough that you can crack\Nthem with both hands, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:16.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,See ya! I hope you can become a seagull as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What was with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Spouting nonsense like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What does he mean, seagull?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,"Ya chaika!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It means "I'm a seagull."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:36.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It was the call sign of the first woman to\Nfly into space, Valentina Tereshkova!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You... That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We should get going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.18,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Number 1710. Make sure not to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.02,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Take this with you. Your room number is 2150.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your room number is 0350. Make sure not to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What's your size?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, SS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There are no SS clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We only brought down to S size.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, S is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:53.52,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Room number 2960. Make sure not to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think they're going to make us do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Some sort of closed-environment test, they said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:06.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! There's no cell phone reception in here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Really?! Geez, how depressing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's still a little too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,0350... 0350...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.61,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.82,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,This is great, Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.45,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,This exam might just be lucky for me!
Comment: 0,0:11:56.27,0:12:06.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.28,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We can't even introduce ourselves if you just stand in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:30.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My name's Oumi Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We're in the same year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm 14 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was bom early in the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How about you, Oumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was bom early as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:58.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry for staring like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Also, you can just call me Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:04.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My name. Don't call me Oumi, call me Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Kei... chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:11.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, you can call me Asumi as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:24.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, I haven't asked the other girl's name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She seems kinda hard to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard with that type of person, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I had heard that there weren't many girls\Nin the Astronaut Training Course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so I was a little anxious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:49.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So I'm not really sure I should say I'm relieved, but I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Trying to get all friendly like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something else you should be doing first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Something I should be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The handle on that door that you just came through...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How many people do you think have touched it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,People checking the room for the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:17.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...applicants who got the wrong room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There have to have been quite a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You clasped that door handle for more than ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:30.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, your right hand is covered in the dirty handprints and bacteria of ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:36.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The first thing that you should do in this\Nclosed environment is keep it clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you shouldn't be shaking hands with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.71,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was listening to all that, but who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That was saying too much no matter how you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, it's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:21.58,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the closed-environment adaptation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:29.21,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After you have confirmed that there are three applicants in your individual rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:33.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...please push the red button next to the door only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Red button?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The door disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll open again if you press the button again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The test has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They didn't tell you to push it twice, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.75,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Use your head before you do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Now, I will explain the details of the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:10.17,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The three members in each room will each be one team...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...and will spend the seven days of this test\Ntogether in this closed environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Se-Seven{Se... Seven} days? In this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:22.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Be quiet. I can't hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:22.14,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,At 9 o'clock at night, the lights will automatically turn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.40,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,At 6 o'clock in the morning, they\Nwill automatically turn back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:31.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Meals and clothes tor the seven days are provided\Nfor you on the shelves next to the beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Please confirm this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's true. They're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:42.87,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You are not to spend the seven days here doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:48.63,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,As a group project, you are to complete something within the seven allotted days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:56.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The project is contained in the white box that is located in the comer of each room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:04.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That box must be opened by inputting the room\Nnumber that your team has been assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.69,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There is no second chance, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:13.40,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Also, if there is an unavoidable reason\Nthat you cannot complete the project...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...or if you are unable to continue either mentally or physically...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...or if there is an emergency situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:26.58,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...you can stop the test and open the door by\Npressing the red button mentioned earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:32.38,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,However, no matter what the circumstances, if\Nyou push this button again in these seven days...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:36.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...all three members of the team will fail the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.99,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Those teams who have already pressed the button again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If this were the real thing you would already have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:47.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This one time only, we will simply treat\Nthis as a demerit against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.52,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Good luck in your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:56.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you even planning on doing anything, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:07.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You slept through the whole explanation without listening at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I just haven't gotten enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My girlfriend just wouldn't let me sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:19.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So you're gonna say that your bruise there is\Nbecause she hit you, saying not to go, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, bringing up nonsense like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:36.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I never said you could go to that school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:46.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, the "saying not to go" part was certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So, what are we doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This guy really wasn't listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:56.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The project for the test is inside of this box...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:00.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but it won't open until you input the room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We only have one chance, so no trying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:07.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's why they said not to forget our room numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The person typing it in will have a grave responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:14.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What, leaving it to others again, you eyebrow-shaving jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:18.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I have a great name, Suzuki Shuu, that you can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Understand my great style, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What great style is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So, can you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:29.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I remembered the owl so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:32.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The owl that goes "hoot, hoot"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You could remember Sagittarius as well, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Would you cut this stuff out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:43.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What connection is there between an owl and a constellation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if I push it wrong, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.90,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why the room numbers\Nwere all mixed up like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't remember everything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:07.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really? Nice going, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hold on one second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:16.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't trust you enough to {}leave my fate to you{entrust you with my fate} just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Fate!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:20.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You've been making too big a deal of this the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,First off, does that mean that you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It will definitely be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,l can say that with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:36.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, you really do remember it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then I'll leave it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Although it doesn't really matter, since I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, who's the one leaving things to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:16.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So, what's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:36.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How many times did you press the button right\Nwhen I was telling you not to, you moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:39.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you forgot the room number too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:43.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's easy to forget such random numbers like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like this is a quiz show or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:59.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:02.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:08.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I-It's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:16.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:18.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:20.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try helping us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:34.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Domino pieces...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:37.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The secondary exam of the Astronaut Training Course...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:41.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Days of doing nothing but lining up dominoes behind closed doors...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.02,0:24:45.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Our three lives are filled with nervousness,\Ncarrying on with impatience.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:47.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then, when we thought that the test would end this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.94,0:24:51.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...something we never expected to happen\Ntakes place on the fourth day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.74,0:24:53.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:57.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: Memory of a Distant Day.